## Limitations
The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of individual effectiveness in organizations. The information is limited to the perspectives and findings of the cited sources, which may not encompass the full range of strategies employed across different industries and organizational cultures. Additionally, some sources may not be peer-reviewed, which could affect the reliability of the information.